# shfmt configuration for consistent shell script formatting
# https://github.com/mvdan/sh#shfmt

# Use 2-space indentation (standard for most projects)
-i 2

# Indent case statement cases for better readability
-ci

# Simplify code where possible (remove unnecessary syntax)
-s

# Keep padding for column alignment (preserves manual formatting)
-kp

# Note: This configuration provides consistent, readable formatting
# while preserving intentional code structure and alignment.